				<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/63f452d6f5ac21ca0c0cef8ce9f4bdc0?s=44&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' />				<cite class="comment-author">channy</cite>
