			<div class="comment-content comment">
				<p>Superbe article.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="comment-action">
				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2013/03/11/21737-les-impots-grimpent-la-grogne-aussi?replytocom=105324#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-105324", "105324", "respond", "21737")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
